    "text": "# April 16, 2026  \n- Morning started with Browny barking at the mailman. Preeti was still sleeping.\n- Dropped Neetish at school on the way to office. She forgot her water bottle.\n- Office: major client presentation went well. Boss appreciated the team's work.\n- Lunch with colleagues at the canteen. Discussed the upcoming cricket match.\n- Preeti called: Mohan had a fever. She took him to the doctor.\n- Left office early to check on Mohan. He was fine, just a viral.\n- Evening: gave the kids a bath. Browny tried to jump in the tub.\n- Preeti made dal chawal. Simple but tasty.\n- Bedtime story for Mohan. He requested a dragon story again.\n- Planning the weekend trip to the mall with family.",
